75
00:04:51,490 --> 00:04:54,770
Well an embedded system
is typically reactive.

76
00:04:54,770 --> 00:04:59,310
This means that such system is constantly
interacting with its environment and

77
00:04:59,310 --> 00:05:01,910
executes with that environment say so.

78
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:07,840
