and transits to a new state.

80
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:17,190
Thus such systems can
be modeled as Automata.

81
00:05:17,190 --> 00:05:21,450
In other words, it is a set of states,
inputs, and outputs.

82
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:27,680
