system consists of inputs,

83
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:31,090
outputs, a unit to perform computations,
and

84
00:05:31,090 --> 00:05:36,180
communication interfaces to exchange
data with other embedded systems.

85
00:05:36,180 --> 00:05:38,890
Inputs provide the computation
unit with data.

86
00:05:39,940 --> 00:05:42,380
Sensors can play the role of inputs.

87
00:05:42,380 --> 00:05:45,790
Sensors can convert physical
quantities into numbers.

88
00:05:47,290 --> 00:05:50,710
Actuators for example,
electrical moderators can be outputs.

89
00:05:51,860 --> 00:05:56,730
In between inputs and outputs there
is a unit called processing element

90
00:05:56,730 --> 00:06:00,700
that makes computations on the input and
produces output.

91
00:06:02,110 --> 00:06:05,380
